snippet.textDisplay:
If Yoongi happens to see this:


After listening to INTERLUDE SHADOW for all day and night, and loving it so very much, I wanted to make an effort to say a BIG thank you to you.
Thank you for creating this masterpiece and for gifting us with such diversity, and thank you for allowing us to have a sneak-peak inside your soul.

I know it isn't easy to bare your feelings, to throw out those raw emotions and not be scared.
I know that it must have been tough going through everything you went, and finally winning over everything, and coming out as a KING, as a ROCKSTAR that you are.

The you that is SUGA, who was born to be the genius RAP STAR, and the one who dominates the chart with his fire spitting verses, and always trying his best to give fans the best piece of his mind, and soul, as much as possible - THANK YOU for creating this rap piece.
The you that is YOONGI, who was born to be a genius producer, a sweet hyung, a devoted workoholic (I say devoted, because you truly love what you do and that you wouldn't have it any other way), and also a great inspiration for other members - THANK YOU for creating this piece.
I can't express how happy I'm to finally get an idea of what goes on in that beautiful mind of yours.
I know you and the boys love us alot, and always want to give out uplifting songs and music.
But just like how OUTRO:TEAR decorates the pain of a heartbreak,
this song INTERLUDE: SHADOW decorates the fear of the mind, and the eternal fight between the two halves of ones soul, and it is truly BEAUTIFUL.
I loved it, and I am happy that I'm part of a time, where I get to witness such miracles on a daily basis.

I love how you quietly, but surely, slip into our hearts and rule it, always, be it music or otherwise.
I love how you speak a few words, but they are the best advice, the best words of wisdom I have heard from an artist.
Thank you for always wanting to create the music that helps us through dark times, and thank you for holding our hands and helping us walk the lonely road.

THANK YOU for always being real with us, about your difficulties, and about how we should face life. THANK YOU for not sugar-coating things and laying them out in front of us, as it should be.

THANK YOU for supporting us every single day.

I know that the mountain you're climbing has winding paths, and you might get a bit breathless when trying to reach the top. It might be a bit lonely out there too. But please be rest assured that we, the BTS ARMY, will always be holding onto your hand, as you make your way to the top.
And we'll try our best to deal with the demons along side you.
We'll always stand by your side, and hope to be a presence from which you take strength.

THANK YOU for accepting the SHADOWS inside you, and for encouraging us to do the same.

We love you!

After listening to INTERLUDE SHADOW for all day and night, and loving it so very much, I wanted to make an effort to say a BIG thank you to you.
Thank you for creating this masterpiece and for gifting us with such diversity, and thank you for allowing us to have a sneak-peak inside your soul.

I know it isn't easy to bare your feelings, to throw out those raw emotions and not be scared.
I know that it must have been tough going through everything you went, and finally winning over everything, and coming out as a KING, as a ROCKSTAR that you are.

The you that is SUGA, who was born to be the genius RAP STAR, and the one who dominates the chart with his fire spitting verses, and always trying his best to give fans the best piece of his mind, and soul, as much as possible - THANK YOU for creating this rap piece.
The you that is YOONGI, who was born to be a genius producer, a sweet hyung, a devoted workoholic (I say devoted, because you truly love what you do and that you wouldn't have it any other way), and also a great inspiration for other members - THANK YOU for creating this piece.
I can't express how happy I'm to finally get an idea of what goes on in that beautiful mind of yours.
I know you and the boys love us alot, and always want to give out uplifting songs and music.
But just like how OUTRO:TEAR decorates the pain of a heartbreak,
this song INTERLUDE: SHADOW decorates the fear of the mind, and the eternal fight between the two halves of ones soul, and it is truly BEAUTIFUL.
I loved it, and I am happy that I'm part of a time, where I get to witness such miracles on a daily basis.

I love how you quietly, but surely, slip into our hearts and rule it, always, be it music or otherwise.
I love how you speak a few words, but they are the best advice, the best words of wisdom I have heard from an artist.
Thank you for always wanting to create the music that helps us through dark times, and thank you for holding our hands and helping us walk the lonely road.

THANK YOU for always being real with us, about your difficulties, and about how we should face life. THANK YOU for not sugar-coating things and laying them out in front of us, as it should be.

THANK YOU for supporting us every single day.

I know that the mountain you're climbing has winding paths, and you might get a bit breathless when trying to reach the top. It might be a bit lonely out there too. But please be rest assured that we, the BTS ARMY, will always be holding onto your hand, as you make your way to the top.
And we'll try our best to deal with the demons along side you.
We'll always stand by your side, and hope to be a presence from which you take strength.

THANK YOU for accepting the SHADOWS inside you, and for encouraging us to do the same.

We love you!
